First Paragraph (Overview of career)

Vijay is a DevOps and Cloud Engineering professional with over 12 years of IT experience, including 5.7 years in DevOps. He has worked on designing and automating infrastructure, CI/CD pipelines, and cloud deployments across multiple domains such as telecommunications, insurance, and enterprise applications. He is highly skilled in streamlining delivery processes, enhancing system reliability, and collaborating effectively with cross-functional teams.

